Send_Modification_To_Sponsor_Error_Page.heading: You can't send this modification to sponsor

Label_Texts.send_modification_to_sponsor_hint_label: You can't currently send this modification to sponsor as you already have another modification that is either with sponsor or with review body. You can only have one modification with the status 'With sponsor' or 'With review body' at a time. You'll need to wait until a final outcome has been issued before you can submit another.
